## 2. Context 依赖详解

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph AuthContext["AuthContext"]
        direction TB
        A1["user: User | null"]
        A2["session: Session | null"]
        A3["loading: boolean"]
        A4["signIn()"]
        A5["signUp()"]
        A6["signOut()"]
        A7["signInWithGoogle()"]
    end

    subgraph PromptContext["PromptContext"]
        direction TB
        P1["prompts: Prompt[]"]
        P2["categories: Category[]"]
        P3["loading: boolean"]
        P4["error: string | null"]
        P5["fetchPrompts()"]
        P6["createPrompt()"]
        P7["updatePrompt()"]
        P8["deletePrompt()"]
        P9["fetchCategories()"]
        P10["createCategory()"]
        P11["searchPrompts()"]
    end

    subgraph External["外部依赖"]
        supabase["supabase.ts"]
    end

    AuthContext --> supabase
    PromptContext --> supabase
    PromptContext --> AuthContext
```

