## 3. 数据类型依赖

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Prompt {
        +string id
        +string user_id
        +string title
        +string content
        +string | null category_id
        +string[] tags
        +Variable[] variables
        +number usage_count
        +string created_at
        +string updated_at
    }

    class Category {
        +string id
        +string user_id
        +string name
        +string | null parent_id
        +number sort_order
        +string created_at
    }

    class Variable {
        +string name
        +string description
        +string | undefined default_value
    }

    class CreatePromptInput {
        +string title
        +string content
        +string | null category_id
        +string[] tags
        +Variable[] variables
    }

    class CreateCategoryInput {
        +string name
        +string | null parent_id
        +number sort_order
    }

    Prompt --> CreatePromptInput : creates
    Category --> CreateCategoryInput : creates
    Prompt --> Variable : contains
```

