## 4. 页面路由与依赖

```mermaid
graph TD
    Router["React Router<br/>路由配置"]

    Route1["/login<br/>→ LoginPage"]
    Route2["/<br/>→ DashboardPage"]
    Route3["/prompts<br/>→ PromptListPage"]
    Route4["/prompts/:id<br/>→ PromptDetailPage"]
    Route5["/settings<br/>→ SettingsPage"]

    Router --> Route1
    Router --> Route2
    Router --> Route3
    Router --> Route4
    Router --> Route5

    Route1 --> Login["LoginPage"]
    Route2 --> Dashboard["DashboardPage"]
    Route3 --> PromptList["PromptListPage"]
